---
import RootLayout from "@/layouts/root.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import ProfileImage from "@/assets/profile.webp";
---

<RootLayout title="About - Yagnik Patel">
  <main class="mb-8">
    <section class="mb-8 border-b pb-4">
      <div class="flex items-center mb-8">
        <Image
          src={ProfileImage}
          alt="Yagnik Patel"
          width={75}
          height={75}
          loading="eager"
          class="rounded-full mr-4"
        />
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">Yagnik Patel</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <p>
          Hello! I'm Yagnik Patel, a passionate computer science student and aspiring web developer. 
          I'm currently pursuing my degree at New York University, where I'm honing my skills in 
          various programming languages and cutting-edge technologies.
        </p>
        <p>
          My journey in tech began when I built my first website at the age of 14. Since then, 
          I've been captivated by the power of code to solve real-world problems and create 
          meaningful experiences. I'm particularly interested in web development, artificial 
          intelligence, and the intersection of technology and sustainability.
        </p>
        <p>
          When I'm not coding or studying, you can find me exploring the vibrant tech scene 
          in New York City, contributing to open-source projects, or mentoring junior developers. 
          I believe in the power of community and continuous learning in the ever-evolving world of technology.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Interests</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
        <li>Web Development (Frontend and Backend)</li>
        <li>Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning</li>
        <li>Open Source Contribution</li>
        <li>Tech Entrepreneurship</li>
        <li>Cybersecurity</li>
        <li>Sustainable Technology</li>
        <li>Competitive Programming</li>
        <li>UI/UX Design</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </main>
</RootLayout>